      		<p>
      			<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>ma-kō-vicaiya-na
      			<lb n="3" break="no"/>nti-vikkirama-parumaṟkku
      			<lb n="4" break="no"/>yāṇṭu patiṉāṉk-āva
      			<lb n="5" break="no"/>tu
      		</p>
      		<p>
      			pālūr-kōṭṭattu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ḻē
      			<lb n="6" break="no"/><choice><orig>ṉ</orig><reg>n</reg></choice>āṭṭu Ōkūr <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṭṭimaṟu kiḻā
      			<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṉ cēttaṉ makaṉ kuḻaṉ ce
      			<lb n="8" break="no"/>ykai
      		</p>
      		<p>
      			Itu kāṭṭāṉ aṭi
      			<lb n="9"/>eṉ muṭi mēḻaṉa      			
      		</p>      		      		
      		
