         <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
         	
         	<p n="1">
         		<gap reason="lost"/>
         	</p>
         	<p n="2-5">
         		Fourtheenth year of the glorious <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>śrīmant</foreign></supplied> and victorious king Nantivikkiramaparumaṉ.<note>Sanskrit Nandivikramavarman</note>
         	</p>
         	<p n="5-8">
         		<supplied reason="subaudible">This is the</supplied> work <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ceykai</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Kuḻaṉ, son <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Cēttaṉ, landowner <supplied reason="subaudible">in</supplied> <gap reason="lost"/>ṭṭimaṟu <supplied reason="subaudible">in</supplied> Ōkūr, in the <gap reason="lost"/>nāṭu, <supplied reason="subaudible">itself</supplied> in the Pālūrkōṭṭam. 
         	</p>
         	
         	<p n="8-9">
         		The feet of he who protects this <supplied reason="explanation">donation</supplied> are on my head.
         	</p>

